Preheat the oven to 180C/350F/Gas 4.Place the bread in a food processor and pulse to make breadcrumbs.Mix the breadcrumbs with the remaining ingredients in a large bowl until the mixture pulls away from the sides of the bowl and forms a ball.Form the mixture into a loaf shape and place in an ovenproof dish or loaf tin. Bake in the oven for 50â€“60 minutes, or until a skewer inserted into the centre comes out clean.